t%20to%20stand%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20court%20found%20Arion%20Kurtaj%2C%2018%2C%20guilty%20in%20August%20of%20multiple%20accounts%20related%20to%20hacking%20several%20tech%20companies%2C%20including%20Uber%20and%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20releasing%20sensitive%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20first%20arrested%20Kurtaj%20in%20January%202022%2C%20along%20with%20an%20unidentified%2017-year-old.%20They%20released%20the%20pair%20on%20bail%20as%20the%20investigation%20continued.%20Kurtaj%20was%20re-arrested%20in%20March%202022%20and%20placed%20under%20house%20arrest%20in%20a%20Travelodge%20motel%20for%20his%20protection.%20From%20the%20hotel%20room%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fin.ign.com%2Fgrand-theft-auto-vi%2F192702%2Fnews%2Fgta-6-teenage-hacker-found-guilty-of-12-charges-will-be-sentenced-in-future%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanaged%20to%20hack%20into%20Rockstar%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20an%20Amazon%20Fire%20TV%20Stick%20connected%20to%20the%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurtaj%20accessed%20the%20company's%20Slack%20channels%20and%20posted%20a%20message%20that%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Rockstar%20does%20not%20contact%20me%20on%20Telegram%20within%2024%20hours%20I%20will%20start%20releasing%20the%20source%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fuk-news%2F2023%2Fdec%2F21%2Fbritish-teenager-behind-gta-6-hack-receives-indefinite-hospital-order%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20sentencing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20judge%20declared%20Kurtaj%20unfit%20to%20stand%20trial%20due%20to%20severe%20autism%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67663128%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20remanding%20him%20to%20an%20indefinite%20stay%20at%20a%20secure%20hospital%20unless%20doctors%20deem%20him%20no%20longer%20a%20danger.%20The%20judge%20said%20Kurtaj's%20%26qu