85470%5C%22%3Ewas%20stage-managed%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArrest%2C%20Inquiry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20that%20the%20then%20station%20house%20officer%20(SHO)%20of%20Jagraon%20had%20picked%20up%20Kaunke%20from%20his%20home%20on%20December%2012%2C%201992%20but%20released%20him%20upon%20the%20insistence%20of%20villagers%20when%20his%20seven-day-old%20grandson%20died.%20The%20jathedar%20was%20rearrested%20on%20December%2025%2C%201992%2C%20and%20implicated%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20village%20youth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20then%20claimed%20Kaunke%20had%20escaped%20from%20custody%20on%20January%202%2C%201993%2C%20after%20breaking%20a%20constable's%20belt%20to%20which%20his%20handcuffs%20were%20attached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%207%2C%201998%2C%20then%20additional%20director%20general%20of%20police%20(security)%2C%20BP%20Tiwari%2C%20began%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20alleged%20extrajudicial%20murder%20of%20Kaunke%20and%20submitted%20it%20to%20the%20government%20in%201999.%20The%20report%20was%20never%20made%20public%2C%20and%20no%20action%20was%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%2024%20years%20after%20the%20report's%20submission%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Human%20Rights%20Organisation%2C%20a%20body%20formed%20in%201995%20to%20investigate%20alleged%20human%20rights%20abuses%20in%20Punjab%2C%20got%20its%20hands%20on%20the%20report%20and%20shared%20it%20with%20the%20current%20Jathedar%20of%20the%20Akal%20Takht%2C%20Giani%20Raghbir%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tiwari%20concludes%20in%20the%20report%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20all%20the%20circumstances%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20then%20SHO%20and%20now%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Gurmeet%20Singh%20took%20remand%20of%20Bhai%20Gurdev%20Singh%20on%20December%2025%2C%201992%2C%20from%20his%20home%2C%20and%20Kaunke%20never%20returned.%20The%20police%20not%20agreeing%20to%20this%20is%20not%20believable.%20It%20is%20also%20not%20believable%20that%20Kaunke%20was%20arrested%20on%20January%202%2C%201993%2C%20and%20he%20escaped%20after%20breaking%20the%20belt%20of%20the%20police%20constable%20to%20whom%20his%20handcuffs%20were%20attached%20during%20a%20firing%20incident%20between%20militants%20and%20a%20police%20party%20near%20village%20Kania.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20report%20recommended%20a%20case%20against%20then%20Jagraon%20SHO%20Gurmeet%20Singh%20for%20wrongful%20confinement%20and%20falsification%20of%20records%20and%20called%20for%20a%20further%20investigation%20into%20the%20incident.%20It%20also%20recommended%20investigating%20the%20role%20of%20other%20cops%20and%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20police%20claim%20that%20Kaunke%20had%20escaped%20from%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEncounters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgangster-shot-in-leg-in-punjab-in-10th-encounter-by-state-police-in-2-weeks-4716074%5C%22%3Etwo%20encounters%20in%20a%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20as%20part%20of%20its%20ongoing%20crackdown%20on%20gangsters.%20Four%20people%20were%20arrested%20in%20all%2C%20with%20one%20of%20them%20being%20shot%20in%20the%20leg%20as%20he%20opened%20fire%20at%20the%20police%20while%20trying%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20that%2C%20an%20arrested%20gangster%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20exchange%20of%20fire%20with%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20in%20Amritsar%20while%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20encounters%20were%20part%20of%20the%2011%20that%20the%20state%20has%20seen%20in%20just%20the%20past%20two%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703355600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fn5gkcfto_punjab-police-generic_625x300_17_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurdev-singh-kaunke-encounters-rising-ghost-of-30-year-old-disappearance-haunts-