0farmers%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIf%20BJP%20respects%20Chaudhary%20Saheb%2C%20then%20give%20him%20Bharat%20Ratna%20and%20make%20his%2012%20Tughlaq%20Marg%20residence%20a%20memorial.%20During%20farmers'%20movement%2C%20the%20BJP%20insulted%20the%20farmers%20%26amp%3B%20has%20insulted%20the%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20Anil%20Dubey%2C%20a%20party%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703354400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Faotjcpio_charan-singh-statue_625x300_23_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-jat-votes-yogi-adityanath-unveils-chaudhary-charan-singhs-statue-4730406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20unveiled%20a%20statue%20of%20Jat%20leader%20and%20former%20prime%20minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20on%20Saturday%2C%20in%20a%20move%20to%20win%20over%20the%20state's%20Jat%20community%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-jat-votes-yogi-adityanath-unveils-chaudhary-charan-singhs-statue-4730406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-jat-votes-yogi-adityanath-unveils-chaudhary-charan-singhs-statue-4730406%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-jat-votes-yogi-adityanath-unveils-chaudhary-charan-singhs-statue-4730406%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%2012%20Seasons%2C%20Seven%20Specials%20and%20Five%20Live%20Tours%2C%26nbsp%3B%E2%80%98Letterkenny%E2%80%99%20Says%20Goodbye%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703354400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FLetterkenny.MAIN_.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235838843%22%2C%22summary%22