t%3BHome%20Alone%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3BLost%20in%20New%20York%2C%26quot%3B%20revealed%20how%20aggressive%20Trump%20was%20to%20get%20into%20the%20sequel%20to%20the%20hit%20comedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20sequel%2C%20Kevin%20(Macaulay%20Culkin)%20is%20once%20again%20left%20alone%20by%20his%20family%20and%20ends%20up%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20He%20talks%20his%20way%20into%20staying%20at%20the%20glitzy%20Plaza%20Hotel%20and%20has%20another%20encounter%20with%20the%20burglars%20from%20the%20first%20film%2C%20Harry%20(Joe%20Pesci)%20and%20Marv%20(Daniel%20Stern).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20with%20actor%20Macaulay%20Culkin%20at%20the%20Plaza%20hotel%20in%201991.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e04e533855cc244f07ea337%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20with%20actor%20Macaulay%20Culkin%20at%20the%20Plaza%20hotel%20in%201991.%3Cp%3ERon%20Galella%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EColumbus%20said%20the%20production%20team%20dealt%20with%20Trump%20because%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20owned%20the%20Plaza%20Hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20shoot%20in%20the%20lobby%2C%26quot%3B%20Columbus%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BWe%20couldn't%20rebuild%20The%20Plaza%20on%20a%20soundstage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20involved%20with%20the%20movie%20thought%20they%20would%20simply%20pay%20Trump%20a%20fee%2C%20as%20is%20usually%20the%20norm%20when%20shooting%20at%20a%20specific%20location%2C%20and%20everything%20would%20be%20square.%20But%20Trump%20wanted%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20paid%20the%20fee%2C%20but%20he%20also%20said%2C%20'The%20only%20way%20you%20can%20use%20the%20Plaza%20is%20if%20I'm%20in%20the%20movie%2C'%26quot%3B%20Columbus%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20agreed%20to%20put%20him%20in%20the%20movie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20Columbus%20was%20always%20going%20to%20use%20Trump's%20cameo%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20but%20it%20was%20decided%20for%20him%20the%20first%20time%20%26quot%3BLost%20in%20New%20York%26quot%3B%20was%20shown%20to%20an%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20cheered%20when%20Trump%20showed%20up%20on-screen%2C%26quot%3B%20Columbus%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20said%20to%20my%20editor%2C%20'Leave%20him%20in%20the%20movie.%20It's%20a%20moment%20for%20the%20audience.'%20But%20he%20did%20bully%20his%20way%20into%20the%20movie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdonald-trump-home-alone-sequel-director-2020-11%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703351453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e079b05e94e864b2573ca1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdonald-trump-home-alone-sequel-director-2020-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Director%20Chris%20Columbus%20said%20Donald%20Trump%20agreed%20to%20let%20them%20shoot%20in%20his%20hotel's%20lobby%20only%20if%20he%20was%20in%20the%20movie.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jguerrasio%40insider.com%20(Jason%20Guerrasio)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5115%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdonald-trump-home-alone-sequel-director-2020-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20bars%20anti-war%20candidate%20from%20challenging%20Putin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703351100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-yekaterina-duntsova_6399434.jpg%3F20231223171113%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussia-bars-anti-war-candidate-yekaterina-duntsova-from-challenging-president-vladimir-putin-13036870%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20TV%20journalist%20hoping%20to%20challenge%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20Russia's%20next%20presidential%20election%2