20for%20the%20campaign%20and%20the%20party%20setting%20a%20target%20of%20getting%2035%20crore%20votes%20in%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20meeting%20was%20focused%20on%20working%20out%20seat-sharing%20with%20allies%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20to%20take%20on%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Mission%20Mode'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20BJP%20meeting%20of%20national%20office%20bearers%20and%20state%20presidents%2C%20which%20began%20on%20Friday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20asked%20workers%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20mission%20mode.%20Sources%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20set%20the%20party%20a%20target%20of%20winning%2035%20crore%20votes%20in%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20against%20the%2022.9%20crore%20it%20managed%20to%20get%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20meet%2C%20according%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20also%20focused%20on%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20on%20January%2022.%20It%20was%20decided%20that%20workers%20would%20be%20asked%20to%20give%20out%20as%20much%20information%20on%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20as%20possible%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20hold%20discussions%20on%20it.%20They%20will%20also%20be%20instructed%20to%20arrange%20for%20live%20telecast%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20on%20January%2022%20and%20organise%20visits%20to%20Ayodhya%20after%20the%20consecration%20for%20people%20from%20every%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20achieve%20the%20increase%20in%20votes%2C%20a%20strategy%20was%20formulated%20to%20reach%207%20crore%20beneficiaries%20of%20various%20government%20schemes%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20address%20the%20youth%20across%20the%20country%20in%20January%20and%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20run%20a%20campaign%20to%20connect%20with%20women%2C%20youth%2C%20farmers%20and%20the%20poor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20will%20also%20be%20asked%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20every%20voter%20at%20the%20booth%20level%20and%20visit%20their%20homes%20and%20meet%20them.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20issues%20they%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20discuss%20is%20India's%20growing%20power%20on%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlliance%20Panel%20Meet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Alliance%20Committee%20of%20the%20Congress%20held%20its%20first%20meeting%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20five-member%20panel%20was%20formed%20earlier%20this%20week%20to%20discuss%20seat-sharing%20and%20alliances%20with%20other%20political%20parties%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20for%20the%202024%20elections.%20Mukul%20Wasnik%20is%20the%20convenor%20and%20the%20other%20members%20are%20Union%20minister%20Salman%20Khurshid%2C%20former%20chief%20ministers%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20and%20Mohan%20Prakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Wasnik%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20first%20speak%20to%20the%20state%20units.%20We%20will%20decide%20on%20a%20%C2%A0seat-sharing%20formula%20soon.%20There%20is%20no%20deadline%20set%20for%20this.%20But%20we%20will%20decide%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20some%20INDIA%20allies%20after%20its%20defeats%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20elections%2C%20who%20have%20also%20said%20that%20the%20party%20should%20be%20more%20accommodating%20in%20seat-sharing%20conversations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703350800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F86ju07q8_bjp-office-bearers-meeting_625x300_23_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffocus-on-votes-ram-temple-inside-story-of-key-bjp-meeting-4730151%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20behind%20them%2C%20bo