3122300666_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fpolitics%2Fpilot-cong-s-gen-secy-in-charge-of-chhattisgarh-priyanka-replaced-in-up-123122300666_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20Gets%20Its%20First%20Airbus%20350%2C%20Only%20Indian%20Carrier%20To%20Fly%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20officially%20took%20delivery%20of%20its%20first%20Airbus%20A350-900%20today%2C%20making%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20carrier%20to%20operate%20this%20aircraft%20type.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAir%20India%2C%20India's%20leading%20global%20airline%2C%20today%20welcomed%20the%20first%20of%2020%20Airbus%20A350-900%20aircraft%2C%20registered%20VT-JRA%2C%20in%20the%20airline's%20bold%20new%20livery%2C%20marking%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20its%20ongoing%20transformation%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20airline%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20arrived%20in%20New%20Delhi%20at%201%3A46%20pm%20today%20from%20the%20Airbus%20facility%20in%20Toulouse%2C%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delivery%20flight%2C%20operated%20using%20a%20special%20call%20sign%20AI350%2C%20was%20welcomed%20by%20Air%20India%20representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India's%20Senior%20Commander%20Captain%20Monika%20Batra%20Vaidya%2C%20among%20the%20first%20few%20Indian%20pilots%20to%20be%20trained%20on%20A350%2C%20was%20on%20board%20as%20an%20observer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20leads%20the%20way%20in%20catalysing%20the%20renaissance%20of%20Indian%20aviation%2C%20inducting%20the%20first%20new%20wide-body%20fleet%20type%20in%20India%20in%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20airline%20to%20fly%20the%20A350.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20was%20also%20the%20first%20Indian%20airline%20to%20have%20inducted%20the%20Boeing%20787%20Dreamliner%20fleet%20type%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECampbell%20Wilson%2C%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20and%20Managing%20Director%2C%20Air%20India%2C%20said%20that%20the%20moment%20marked%20a%20red-letter%20day%20for%20all%20at%20Air%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20A350%20is%20not%20just%20metal%20and%20engines%3B%20it's%20the%20flying%20embodiment%20of%20the%20relentless%20efforts%20of%20all%20Air%20India%20employees%20towards%20our%20airline's%20continuing%20transformation%20and%20of%20our%20commitment%20to%20setting%20new%20benchmarks.%20It%20is%20also%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20a%20declaration%20of%20Indian%20aviation's%20resurgence%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20new%20age%20of%20flying%2C%20the%20A350%20promises%20a%20world-class%2C%20long-haul%20travel%20experience%20on%20the%20airline's%20non-stop%20routes%2C%20providing%20an%20unparalleled%20level%20of%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20excellent%20flight%20economics%20and%20state-of-the-art%20technology%20underscore%20our%20dedication%20to%20commercially%20successful%20operations%20and%20to%20achieving%20our%20sustainability%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India's%20A350%20will%20enter%20commercial%20service%20in%20January%202024%2C%20initially%20operating%20domestically%20for%20crew%20familiarisation%2C%20followed%20by%20longer-haul%20flying%20to%20destinations%20across%20continents.%20The%20schedule%20of%20commercial%20operations%20with%20the%20A350%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India's%20A350-900%20aircraft%20comes%20in%20a%20three-class%20cabin%20configuration%20with%20316%20seats%20designed%20by%20Collins%20Aerospace%3A%2028%20private%20Business%20Class%20suites%20with%20full-flat%20beds%2C%2024%20Premium%20Economy%20seats%20with%20extra%20legroom%20and%20multiple%20other%20differentiating%20features%2C%20and%20264%20spacious%20Economy%20Class%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20is%20the%20first%20of%20Air%20India's%2020%20Airbus%20A350-900S%20on%20order%2C%20with%20five%20more%20scheduled%20for%20deliveries%20through%20March%202024.%20Air%20India's%20firm%20orders%20for%20250%20new%20aircraft%20with%20Airbus%20include%2020%20A350-1000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20airline%20started%20the%20rollout%20of%20its%20new%20global%20brand%20identity%20across%20guest%20touchpoints%2C%20having%20launched%20a%20new%20consumer-facing%20website%20and%20mobile%20app.%20Last%20week%2C%20the%20airline%20unveiled%20its%20much-anticipated%20new%20collection%20of%20uniforms%20for%20cabin%20and%20cockpit%20crew%20designed%20by%20Indian%20celebrity%20couturier%2C%20Manish%20Malhotra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India's%20cabin%20crew%20and%20pilots%20will%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20new%20uniforms%20starting%20with%20the%20entry%20of%20service%20of%20the%20A350.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Tata-owned%20Air%20India%20has%20outlined%20ambitious%20expansion%20plans%2C%20with%20an%20order%20for%2040%20Airbus%20A350%20aircraft%20set%20to%20be%20integrated%20gradually%20in%20the%20upcoming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20has%20solidified%20its%20order%20for%20250%20Airbus%20aircraft%20and%20220%20new%20Boeing%20flights%2C%20collectively%20valued%20at%20%2470%20billion%20at%20list%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategic%20move%20comes%20as%20the%20airline%20aims%20for%20a%20turnaround%20under%20its%20new%20ownership%2C%20Tata.%20Air%20India%20secured%20purchase%20agreements%20for%20these%20aircraft%20with%20Airbus%20and%20Boeing%20during%20the%20Paris%20Air%20Show%20in%20June%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703347740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fvogp99oo_air-india-a350-x_625