ntent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukraine%20parliament%20has%20adopted%20a%20new%20law%20legalising%20the%20medical%20use%20of%20marijuana%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20help%20treat%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorder%20(PTSD)%20caused%20by%20the%20ongoing%20Russian%20war.%20According%20to%20the%20official%20website%20of%20the%20lawmaking%20body%2C%20the%20parliament%20approved%20the%20bill%20on%20Thursday%20that%20would%20allow%20marijuana%20to%20be%20used%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%20treatment%20of%20oncological%20diseases%20and%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorders%26quot%3B.%20The%20law%20was%20adopted%20with%20284%20votes%20in%20favour%2C%2016%20votes%20against%2C%2033%20abstentions%20and%2040%20members%20not%20voting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20law%20will%20now%20come%20into%20effect%20after%20six%20months%2C%20as%20per%20news%20agency%20ANI.%20The%20law%20would%20regulate%20%26quot%3Bthe%20circulation%20of%20hemp%20plants%20(Cannabis)%20for%20medical%2C%20industrial%20purposes%2C%20scientific%20and%20scientific-technical%20activities%20to%20create%20conditions%20for%20expanding%20patient%20access%20to%20the%20necessary%20treatment%20of%20oncological%20diseases%20and%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorders%2C%20received%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20final%20version%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliament's%20chair%2C%20Ruslan%20Stefanchuk%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20list%20of%20conditions%20and%20ways%20of%20using%20cannabis%20medicines%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possible%20legalisation%20of%20medical%20marijuana%20has%20long%20been%20debated%20in%20Ukraine.%20The%20proposal%20was%20debated%20and%20reviewed%20for%20over%20a%20year%20after%20its%20introduction%20in%202022.%20Ukraine%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20also%20threw%20his%20support%20behind%20the%20push%20for%20the%20legalisation%20of%20medical%20marijuana.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20he%20even%20addressed%20his%20country's%20parliament%20calling%20for%20the%20drug's%20legalisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20finally%20fairly%20legalise%20cannabis-based%20medicines%20for%20all%20those%20who%20need%20them%2C%20with%20appropriate%20scientific%20research%20and%20controlled%20Ukrainian%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Zelensky%20had%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20translation%20from%20the%20local%20press.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20world's%20best%20practices%2C%20all%20the%20most%20effective%20policies%2C%20all%20the%20solutions%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20difficult%20or%20unusual%20they%20may%20seem%20to%20us%2C%20must%20be%20applied%20to%20Ukraine%20so%20that%20Ukrainians%2C%20all%20out%20citizens%2C%20do%20not%20have%20to%20endure%20the%20pain%2C%20stress%20and%20trauma%20of%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20according%20to%20the%20parliament%20website%2C%20the%20Health%20Ministry%20will%20determine%20details%20on%20the%20specific%20conditions%20and%20medicines%20permitted%20under%20the%20new%20law.%20%26quot%3BThe%20law%20provides%20citizens%20with%20access%20to%20the%20necessary%20treatment%20for%20serious%20illnesses%2C%20including%20cancer%20and%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorders%20caused%20by%20war.%20The%20list%20of%20conditions%20and%20methods%20of%20using%20cannabis%20medicines%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20website%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703345760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Fhefqtu1o_marijuana_625x300_20_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fukraine-legalises-medical-marijuana-to-help-ease-stress-from-russia-war-4729743%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ukraine%20parliament%20has%20adopted%20a%20new%20law%20legalising%20the%20medical%20use%20of%20marijuana%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20help%20tre