ople%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%20were%20currently%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttempts%20to%20evaluate%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20humanitarian%20work%20in%20Gaza%20based%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20aid%20entering%20the%20territory%20are%20mistaken%2C%20Guterres%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20way%20Israel%20is%20conducting%20this%20offensive%20is%20creating%20massive%20obstacles%20to%20the%20distribution%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20inside%20Gaza%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20effective%20aid%20operation%20in%20Gaza%20requires%20security%3B%20staff%20who%20can%20work%20in%20safety%3B%20logistical%20capacity%3B%20and%20the%20resumption%20of%20commercial%20activity.%20These%20four%20elements%20do%20not%20exist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20humanitarian%20workers%20who%20were%20in%20the%20strip%20were%20facing%20a%20struggle%20to%20survive%20whilst%20also%20helping%20expand%20operations%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20miracle%20that%20they%20have%20been%20able%20to%20continue%20working%20under%20these%20conditions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuterres%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20just%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-security-council-passes-resolution-on-war-in-gaza-us-russia-abstain%5C%22%3EUN%20Security%20Council%20passed%20a%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20demanding%20unobstructed%20humanitarian%20work%20in%20Gaza%20and%20calling%20for%20a%20way%20to%20be%20paved%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccessation%20of%20hostilities%E2%80%9D%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20did%20not%20demand%20an%20immediate%20end%20to%20the%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20by%20an%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20reporter%20if%20Guterres%20had%20hoped%20the%20resolution%20would%20agree%20with%20his%20call%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fsg%2Fen%2Fc