%20University%20Graduate%20School%20of%20Design%20and%20resident%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20Logan%20International%20Airport%20for%20a%20flight%20to%20India%20to%20reunite%20with%20her%20family%20when%20her%20Lyft%20driver%20abruptly%20cancelled%20the%20ride%2C%20took%20all%20her%20luggage%20and%20left%20stranded%20on%20the%20road.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fshreya-verma-873134173_lyft-emergency-urgent-activity-7141934279424462848-cTcJ%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Shreya's%20nightmare%20began%20when%20she%20noticed%20she%20had%20forgotten%20to%20bring%20her%20headphones%20after%20her%20trip%20with%20Lyft%20had%20just%20started.%20She%20hurriedly%20recovered%20her%20headphones%20after%20requesting%20the%20driver%20to%20return%20to%20her%20home%20and%20wait.%20However%2C%20upon%20her%20return%2C%20she%20discovered%20that%20the%20driver%20cancelled%20the%20ride%20and%20her%20luggage%20was%20gone.%20This%20sudden%20cancellation%20of%20the%20ride%20meant%20that%20the%20student%20was%20left%20without%20access%20to%20the%20vehicle%20information%20and%20wasn't%20able%20to%20immediately%20track%20down%20her%20belongings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shreya%20shared%20her%20nightmarish%20situation%20on%20LinkedIn.%20She%20even%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20the%20conversations%20she%20had%20with%20Lyft%20customer%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20at%206%20PM%2C%20I%20booked%20a%20ride%20to%20Boston%20airport.%20Shockingly%2C%20after%20loading%20my%20luggage%2C%20the%20driver%20abruptly%20canceled%2C%20leaving%20with%20all%20my%20belongings%2C%20including%20my%20passport%2C%20VISA%2C%20OPT%2FEAD%20Card%2C%20and%20vital%20document%2C%20electronics%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20devastating%20loss%20of%20%2430%2C000%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Shreya%20wrote%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20actively%20seeking%20assistance%20from%20Lyft%20customer%20service%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20crucial%20driver%20details%20remain%20elusive%2C%20compounding%20the%20challenges%20I%20am%20already%20facing%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-american-ceo-calls-for-longer-work-hours-asks-employees-to-blend-work-with-life-4724575%5C%22%3EIndian-American%20CEO%20Calls%20For%20Longer%20Work%20Hours%2C%20Asks%20Employees%20To%20Blend%20Work%20With%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20student%20revealed%20that%20despite%20active%20engagement%20with%20the%20Cambridge%20Police%20Department%20and%20The%20Corporation%20of%20the%20City%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20lack%20of%20pertinent%20information%20is%20hindering%20progress.%20%26quot%3BThe%20mandated%20legal%20procedures%2C%20involving%20subpoenas%2C%20court%20orders%2C%20and%20search%20warrants%2C%20are%20proving%20to%20be%20time-consuming%20and%20emotionally%20taxing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shreya%20shared%20her%20experience%20almost%20a%20week%20back%2C%20and%20since%20it%20has%20gone%20viral%20online.%20It%20prompted%20the%20official%20LinkedIn%20profile%20of%20Lyft%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20post.%20%26quot%3BHi%20Shreya%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20ongoing%20support%20as%20we%20work%20to%20resolve%20this.%20We're%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20driver%20and%20working%20swiftly%20to%20get%20this%20solved%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20commented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELyft%20CEO%20David%20Risher%20also%20reacted%20to%20Ms%20Shreya's%20unfortunate%20incident.%20%26quot%3BVery%20sorry%20you're%20going%20through%20this%2C%20Shreya.%20That's%20absolutely%20awful.%20Our%20team%20is%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Risher%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20unfortunate%20incident%2C%20however%2C%20has%20prevented%20Ms%2