hmir's%20Poonch%20district%20has%20evoked%20condemnation%20and%20protests%20by%20political%20parties%20demanding%20justice%20for%20victims.%20The%20three%20men%20were%20found%20dead%20on%20Friday%20hours%20after%20they%20were%20detained%20for%20questioning%20by%20the%20army.%20At%20least%20seven%20other%20villagers%2C%20who%20were%20also%20detained%2C%20have%20been%20injured%20and%20shifted%20to%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20dozen%20men%20from%20Gujjar%20community%20were%20detained%20a%20day%20after%20major%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20army%20in%20which%20four%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20and%20three%20others%20were%20injured.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20army%20said%20search%20operations%20are%20on%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20under%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETerrorist%20Initiated%20Incident%20at%20Bafliaz%20in%20Poonch-Rajouri%20Sector%20(21%2F%2022%20Dec%2023).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSearch%20operations%20by%20the%20Security%20Forces%20are%20continuing%20in%20the%20area%20of%20operations%20after%20the%20incident%20of%2021%20Dec%2023.%20Reports%20have%20been%20received%20regarding%20three%20civilian%20deaths%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20matter%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKLwtC2C2nm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKLwtC2C2nm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ADG%20PI%20-%20INDIAN%20ARMY%20(%40adgpi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadgpi%2Fstatus%2F1738548583769759899%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETension%20gripped%20the%20area%20after%20the%20deaths%20and%20internet%20services%20have%20been%20suspended%20in%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts.%20A%20larger%20number%20of%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20Bafliaz%20and%20Surankote%20areas%20to%20prevent%20any%20protests%20and%20roads%20leading%20to%20Bafliaz%20have%20also%20been%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20today%20said%20that%20legal%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20the%20incident%20and%20announced%20compensation%20for%20the%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20death%20of%20three%20civilians%20was%20reported%20yesterday%20in%20Baffliaz%20of%20Poonch%20District.%20The%20medico%20legal%20formalities%20were%20conducted%20and%20legal%20action%20in%20this%20matter%20has%20been%20initiated%20by%20the%20appropriate%20authority%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20administration%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20amid%20ongoing%20operation%20to%20track%20down%20terrorists%20behind%20the%20attack%2C%20over%20a%20dozen%20men%20in%20Bufliaz%20area%20were%20detained%20by%20troops%20in%20full%20media%20glare.%20They%20were%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20military%20station%20for%20questioning.%20In%20the%20evening%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20three%20men%20--%20Showkat%20Hussain%20and%20Reyaz%20Ahmad%2C%20Mohammad%20Safeer%20have%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20and%20Apni%20party%20held%20protests%20against%20civilian%20killings%2C%20demanding%20justice%20for%20victims.%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20PDP%20leader%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20claimed%20bodies%20of%20victims%20had%20torture%20marks%20and%20some%20villagers%20were%20detained%20for%20questioning%20are%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20internet%20shutdown%20in%20the%20region%20was%20also%20necessitated%20after%20a%20video%20went%20viral%20showing%20people%20being%20beaten%20and%20tortured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20four%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20and%20three%20others%20were%20injured%20after%20terrorists%20targeted%20two%20army%20vehicles%20on%20Bafliaz%20-Thanamadi%20road.%20While%20a%20massive%20counter%20terrorist%20operation%20was%20launched%2C%20it%20appears%20terrorists%20have%20managed%20to%20escape%20taking%20advantage%20of%20dense%20forests%20and%20treacherous%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerrorist%20group%20Peoples%20Anti-Fascist%20Front%20or%20PAFF%2C%20a%20front%20for%20Lashkar%20e%20Toiba%2C%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%20and%20released%20pictures%20of%20the%20attack%20indicating%20they%20filmed%20the%20gunfight%20with%20body-cams.%20The%20PAFF%20is%20known%20to%20use%20body%20cameras%20footage%20for%20propaganda.%20A%20search%20is%20underway%20for%20the%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20PAFF%20attacked%20an%20army%20truck%20in%20Poonch%20and%20filmed%20it.%20After%20the%20attack%2C%20police%20and%20security%20forces%20detained%20a%20large%20number%20of%20locals.%20One%20Mukhtar%20Hussain%20Shah%20committed%20suicide%20after%20alleging%20harassment%20and%20humiliation%20by%20security%20forces.%20Before%20his%20death%2C%20Shah%20left%20a%20video%20message%20in%20which%20he%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20help%20army%20in%20its%20fight%20against%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703338380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffde35vpg_poonch-civilians-killed_625x300_23_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-civilians-killed-near-j-k-encounter-site-internet-shut-in-2-districts-4729093%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20three%20men%20were%20found%20dead%20on%20Friday%20hours%20after%20they%20were%20detained%20for%20questioning%20by%20the%20army.%20At%20least%20seven%20other%20villagers%20who%20were%20also%20detained%20have%20been%20injured%20and%20shifted%20to%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-civilians-killed-near-j-k-encounter-site-internet-shut-in-2-districts-4729093%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-n