ation%20Limited%2C%20as%20telling%20reporters%20in%20Uttarkashi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERight%20after%20the%20trapped%20workers%20were%20rescued%20on%20November%2028%2C%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20Union%20minister%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20(MoRTH)%2C%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20government%20would%20conduct%20a%20safety%20audit%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fgeological-report-on-tunnel-shows-weak-rock-slip-circle-failure-near-silkyara-101701086300485.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2027%20that%20a%20geological%20report%20submitted%20to%20the%20MoRTH%20before%20construction%20work%20on%20the%20Silkyara-Barkot%20tunnel%20project%20began%20showed%20that%20the%20proposed%20tunnel%20could%20%E2%80%9Cencounter%20weak%20rocks%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20adequate%20support%20structures%20would%20be%20required%20to%20prop%20up%20the%20weak%20rocks.%20An%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20had%20recommended%20that%20a%203.5%20m%20escape%20tunnel%20be%20put%20in%20place%20during%20the%20construction%2C%20but%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdue-to-cost-and-time-concerns-silkyara-tunnel-project-said-no-to-separate-escape-tunnel-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20found%20that%20this%20was%20not%20done%20due%20to%20cost%20and%20time%20constraints.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2041%20workers%20who%20were%20trapped%20at%20the%20Silkyara%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%20for%2017%20days%20have%20each%20been%20awarded%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20%E2%80%93%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3