0send%20a%20message%20of%20impunity%20and%20freedom%20to%20those%20who%20violate%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20hope%20that%20the%20protests%20led%20by%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20would%20yield%20results%20in%20the%20form%20of%20punishment%20to%20Braj%20Bhushan%20Singh%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20his%20presidentship%20of%20the%20WFI%2C%20was%20buried%20when%20the%20results%20of%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20WFI%20were%20announced%20on%C2%A0%20December%2021%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20the%20results%20mark%20a%20closure%20to%20the%20serious%20issues%20raised%20by%20women%20wrestlers%20with%20support%20from%20their%20male%20colleagues%3F%20Does%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20as%20it%20played%20out%20over%202023%20hold%20out%20hope%20for%20those%20who%20would%20like%20to%20see%20the%20premier%20sports%20bodies%20in%20India%20become%20more%20democratic%20and%20representative%20of%20the%20changing%20aspirations%20of%20a%20young%20India%20where%20the%20best%20talent%20has%20sprung%20from%20some%20of%20the%20most%20underprivileged%20social%20groups%3F%20In%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20this%20reality%2C%20the%20sports%20bodies%20remain%20mired%20either%20in%20the%20antics%20of%20a%20bygone%20era%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20own%20version%20of%20%3Cem%3Eparivaarvaad%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20sports%20minister%20held%20in%20June%202023%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20had%20put%20forward%20five%20demands.%20These%20were%20that%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20be%20arrested%20given%20the%20charges%20against%20him%2C%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20to%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20woman%20chief%20of%20the%20WFI%2C%20and%20that%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20or%20his%20family%20members%20should%20not%20be%20part%20of%20the%20WFI.%20They%20had%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20police%20case%20filed%20against%20them%20in%20May%2C%20the%20day%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20parliament%20building%20was%20inaugurated%2C%20be%20scrapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03135106%2FFxNeRGbakAYEoSI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03135106%2FFxNeRGbakAYEoSI.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03135106%2FFxNeRGbakAYEoSI-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03135106%2FFxNeRGbakAYEoSI-1024x686.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-656362%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20stop%20protesting%20wrestlers%20from%20marching%20to%20new%20parliament%20building%20on%20May%2028.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40SakshiMalik%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20the%20Delhi%20police%20%E2%80%93%20which%20had%20delayed%20registration%20of%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20accused%20in%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20law%20and%20only%20after%20the%20matter%20went%20to%20court%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20gave%20ample%20time%20to%20the%20accused%20to%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20complainants%2C%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20alacrity%20shown%20in%20registering%20cases%20against%20the%20protestors.%20As%20on%20an%20earlier%20occasion%2C%20assurances%20were%20given%20to%20the%20protestors%20by%20the%20concerned%20(sic!)%20minister%20clearly%2C%20none%20of%20these%20have%20been%20fulfilled.%20Nor%20has%20any%20action%20been%20reportedly%20taken%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20failure%20to%20uphold%20the%20promise%20made%20to%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers%20that%20Singh%20and%20his%20associates%20would%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20contest%20by%20the%20sports%20minister%2Fministry%20gives%20the%20signal%20of%20impunity%20to%20those%20violating%20the%20law.%20The%20result%20was%20there%20for%20all%20to%20see%20when%20Sakshi%20Malik%20hung%20up%20her%20boots%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20in%20Delhi%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20was%20ever%20any%20doubt%20that%20sexual%20harassment%20is%20a%20crime%20steeped%20and%20soaked%20in%20power%2C%20perhaps%20the%20WFI%20saga%20will%20dispel%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrestlers-protest-to-wfi-elections-recap-of-what-happened-in-12-months-101703168955051-amp.html%5C%22%3Etimeline%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20this%20heroic%20and%20unprecedented%20struggle%20by%20the%20wrestlers%20against%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20is%20forgotten%2C%20the%20visuals%20will%20continue%20to%20tell%20the%20story%3A%20of%20the%20courage%20shown%20by%20those%20who%20chose%20to%20speak%20up%3B%20of%20the%20families%2C%20farmers%20and%20women%20activists%20who%20came%20out%20in%20support%20to%20express%20their%20anger%20in%20public%3B%20of%20the%20police%20alternatively%20choosing%20to%20look%20the%20other%20way%2C%20shunning%20its%20duty%20and%20taking%20measures%20to%20arrest%20the%20protestors%20post%20haste%2C%20at%20the%20beck%20and%20call%20of%20their%20superiors.%20This%20record%20shall%20include%20the%20inglorious%20record%20of%20the%20official%20apathy%20and%20indifference%20to%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers%20while%20showing%20overeagerness%20to%20shield%20those%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20migrants%20during%20Corona%20captured%20in%20the%20visuals%20of%20the%20period%2C%20the%20footage%20of%20Olympians%20and%20international%20sports%20champions%20being%20dragged%20on%20the%20streets%20outside%20even%20as%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20was%20being%20inaugurated%20on%20May%2028%20will%20go%20down%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20the%20numerous%20successes%20of%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%20These%20pictures%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20prime%20accused%20strutting%20about%20with%20full%20freedom%20in%20the%20newly%20inaugurated%20Parliament%20building%20even%20as%20the%20cries%20for%20justice%20of%20those%20who%20had%20brought%20fame%20and%20glory%20to%20the%20country%20could%20be%20heard%20outside%20%E2%80%93%20will%20challenge%20viewers%20to%20read%20the%20sub-text%20of%20the%20achievements%20on%20the%20governance%20front%20in%20India%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Vishwaguru%20in%20the%20times%20to%20come.%20Perhaps%20they%20will%20tell%20us%20more%20than%20the%20media%20analysts%20will%2C%20in%20times%20when%20those%20spinning%20the%20most%20successful%20yarns%20are%20bestowed%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20appointing%20fact-check%20bodies%20on%20whether%20online%20information%20related%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbrij-bhushan-singhs-loyalist-elected-as-the-chief-of-wrestling-federation-of-india%5C%22%3ESakshi%20Malik%20Quits%20Wrestling%20as%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Loyalist%20Elected%20as%20WFI%20Chief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20lessons%20to%20be%20learnt%20from%20these%20unfolding%20events.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20women%20in%20India%20have%20a%20long%20wait%20ahead%20for%20rampant%20sexual%20harassment%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20a%20crime%20to%20be%20tackled%20head-on.%20The%20chances%20for%20women%20to%20get%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20and%20enjoy%20equality%20look%20more%20dim%20as%20this%20year%20ends%2C%20than%20they%20did%20in%20January%202023%2C%20when%20the%20star%20sportspersons%20first%20spoke%20up.%20Clearly%2C%20the%20crime%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20buried%20under%20the%20brazen%20might%20of%20power%20and%20the%20struggle%20to%20bring%20it%20out%20in%20the%20open%20shall%20perhaps%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20a%20Verma%20Committee%2C%20which%20had%20argued%20that%20Army%20men%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20cover%20under%20AFSPA.%20The%20Justice%20Verma%20Committee%20had%20opined%20that%20%E2%80%9CPersonnel%20guilty%20of%20sexual%20offences%20in%20conflict%20areas%20should%20be%20tried%20under%20ordinary%20criminal%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sharp%20contrast%20with%20the%20spirit%20displayed%20at%20that%20time%2C%20the%20impunity%20with%20which%20those%20accused%20in%20the%20WFI%20case%20may%20get%20away%20speaks%20of%20the%20turn%20of%20events%20in%20this%20country.%20The%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20then-unknown%20young%20woman%2C%20given%20the%20name%20of%20Nirbhaya%20by%20the%20media%2C%20shocked%20the%20nation%20and%20led%20to%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Law%20Amendments%20enacted%20in%202013%2C%20followed%20by%20POSH.%20In%20contrast%20with%20the%20response%20in%202013%2C%20the%20cries%20of%20internationally%20acclaimed%20sportspersons%20for%20justice%20were%20sought%20to%20be%20silenced%20with%20the%20force%20of%20might.%20Amidst%20much%20else%20that%20they%20do%2C%20those%20in%20government%2C%20entrusted%20as%20per%20law%20with%20the%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20those%20guilty%20of%20the%20crime%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20are%20punished%2C%20continue%20to%20preach%20to%20ordinary%20mortals%20about%20their%20duty%20towards%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20solidarity%20with%20the%20struggling%20wrestlers%2C%20who%20for%20now%20stand%20defeated%20and%20demoralised%2C%20women%20in%20India%20should%20set%20aside%20a%20special%20day%2F%20date%20to%20mark%20the%20need%20for%20continued%20struggle%20on%20this%20issue.%20Punishment%20of%20those%20guilty%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20is%20a%20critical%20need%20if%20women%20are%20to%20advance%20their%20struggle%20for%20equality%2C%20including%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20work%20and%20employment.%20It%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20realised%20that%20measures%20such%20as%20reservations%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20in%20the%20legislatures%20will%20have%20meaning%20only%20if%20laws%20enacted%20to%20give%20strength%20to%20women%20are%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20contours%20of%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20do%20not%20encompass%20upholding%20the%20dignity%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20sportswomen.%20That%20requires%20both%20political%20will%20on%20the%20part%20of%20governments%20in%20power%20as%20also%20power%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20people%20to%20hold%20governments%20and%20officials%20accountable.%20The%20saga%20of%20the%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20struggle%20against%20sexual%20harassment%20%E2%80%93%20spread%20over%20the%20year%202023%20%E2%80%93%20underlines%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20struggle%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20women%20and%20punishment%20for%20those%20accused%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20is%20integrally%20linked%20to%20the%20struggle%20for%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20so%20in%20times%20when%20democratically%20elected%20governments%20and%20their%20representatives%20choose%20to%20stand%20with%20those%20seen%20to%20be%20violating%20the%20law.%20The%20years%20to%20come%20may%20tell%20us%20more%20about%20how%20women%20in%20India%20look%20beyond%20the%20rhetorical%20invocation%20of%20tradition%20and%20false%20narratives%20of%20history%20to%20make%20constitutional%20guarantees%20a%20part%20of%20their%20everyday%20struggle%20for%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndu%20Agnihotri%20is%20an%20independent%20researcher%2C%20formerly%20Professor%20and%20Director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Development%20Studies%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703328844000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21155114%2FEffect-38.png%22%2C%22originID%