com%2Findia-news%2Fwrestler-bajrang-punia-says-he-is-returning-his-padma-shri-to-pm-modi-amid-wrestling-body-row-4722726%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20are%20not%20given%20due%20respect%2C%20I%20do%20not%20deserve%20this%20honour%20either.%20We%20were%20on%20the%20road%20for%2040%20days%2C%20but%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20government%20have%20not%20been%20fulfilled.%20Our%20fight%20is%20not%20against%20the%20government%2C%20but%20against%20an%20individual.%20I%20believe%20in%20the%20judiciary%20but%2C%20with%20what%20is%20happening%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20keep%20faith%20in%20the%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20not%20give%20up%20wrestling.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20not%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20my%20wrestling%20career%2C%20and%20I%20am%20preparing%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20open%20letter%20to%20Modi%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CSports%20have%20empowered%20our%20women%20athletes%20and%20changed%20their%20lives%20but%20the%20situation%20is%20such%20that%20the%20women%20who%20could%20have%20been%20the%20brand%20ambassadors%20of%20Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%20are%20now%20leaving%20the%20sport.%20And%20we%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20who%20were%20awarded%2C%20could%20not%20do%20anything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sanjay%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20election%20as%20WFI%20chief%2C%20his%20letter%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CWe%20shed%20tears%20the%20entire%20night.%20We%20did%20not%20understand%20what%20to%20do%20or%20where%20to%20go.%20The%20government%20has%20given%20us%20a%20lot.%20I%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%202019%20and%20I%20also%20received%20the%20Arjuna%20and%20Khel%20Ratna%20awards.%20When%20I%20got%20these%20awards%2C%20I%20was%20on%20cloud%20nine.%20But%20today%20the%20sadness%20weighs%20more%20and%20the%20reason%20is%20a%20women%20wrestler%20left%20the%20sport%20because%20of%20(fears%20over)%20her%20security.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20official%20provision%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98return%E2%80%99%20of%20Padma%20awards.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20someone%20sought%20to%20%E2%80%98return%E2%80%99%20their%20award%3B%20in%202020%2C%20former%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Prakash%20Singh%20Badal%20%E2%80%98returned%E2%80%99%20his%20Padma%20award%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20enacted%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20an%20awardee%20may%20announce%20his%20decision%20to%20return%20the%20award%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20Padma%20Awards%20regulations%20do%20not%20cover%20this%20eventuality.%20They%20only%20allow%20cancellation%20and%20annulment%20of%20the%20awards%20by%20the%20President%2C%20without%20specifying%20the%20grounds.%20The%20awardee%20continues%20to%20be%20in%20the%20register%20of%20Padma%20recipients%20maintained%20under%20directions%20of%20the%20President%2C%20until%20his%2Fher%20award%20is%20annulled.%20The%20rules%20provide%20for%20cancellation%20of%20such%20annulment%20by%20the%20President%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fone-can-check-out-in-padma-protest-but-can-never-leave%2Farticleshow%2F106222382.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703313900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23120753%2FEffect-42.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcant-live-as-padma-shri-awardee-when-women-wrestlers-are-insulted-bajrang-punia-to-pm-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Olympic-medal%20winner%20was%20stopped%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20Friday%20when%20he%20set%20out%20to%20return%20his%20award%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20his%20residence.%20He%20left%20his%20Padma%20Shri%20medallion%20on%20a%20footpath%2C%20which%20the%20police%20picked%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcant-live-as-padma-shri-awardee-when-women-wrestlers-are-insulted-bajrang-punia-to-pm-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20LK%20Advani's%20(Sour)%20Grapes%20of%20Rath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fmodi-advani-e1642151298688.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Temple%20Trust%20has%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F701a460e-bcc6-406a-9b40-3d6d87e4c677%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDUifQ.TijM4u7l694OwF41E05LPsDisJEAY4GlxbF7Xh_iCLM%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%98requested%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20veteran%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leaders%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20not%20to%20come%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Maryada%20Purshottam%20Shri%20Ram%20Janambhoomi%20Mandir%20on%20January%2022.%20They%20are%20%E2%80%9Celders%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20family%2C%20a%20Trust%20official%20said%2C%20and%20because%20of%20their%20age%20and%20health%20they%20were%20advised%20to%20stay%20away.%20Advani%20is%2096%20and%20Joshi%20will%20turn%2090%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20touching%20concern%20for%20their%20health%20was%20apparently%20not%20shared%20by%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%2C%20which%20promptly%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F040a9241-5ed1-4adc-9299-a089371b8147%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDUifQ.TijM4u7l694OwF41E05LPsDisJEAY4GlxbF7Xh_iCLM%5C%22%3E%C2%A0invited%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0both%20to%20come.%20So%20now%20the%20decision%20lies%20with%20these%20two%20elders.%20Will%20they%20show%20up%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20a%20downfall%20it%20has%20been%20for%20both%2C%20especially%20Advani%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20whose%20yatra%20in%201990%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20next%20month%E2%80%99s%20inauguration.%20Setting%20out%20in%20his%20Toyota%20converted%20into%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Erath%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20chariot%2C%20he%20toured%20the%20country%20campaigning%20for%20a%20Ram%20temple%20in%20place%20of%20the%20Masjid%20which%20had%20stood%20there%20for%20400%20years%2C%20leaving%20death%20and%20destruction%20in%20his%20wake%2C%20mainly%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%201992%2C%20the%20Masjid%20was%20brought%20down%20%E2%80%94%20a%20telling%20image%20then%20is%20of%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20hugging%20Uma%20Bharati%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20followed%2C%20which%20engulfed%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F27153406%2Fbabri_masjid-11302_2486082a-e1563521469520.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-264285%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992.%20Photo%3A%20Sanjay%20Sharma%2FINDIAPIX%20NETWORK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20gains%20became%20clear%20soon%20after%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20government%20was%20formed%20in%201995%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20BJP-led%20coalition%20in%20Delhi%2C%20headed%20by%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20in%201996.%20He%20remained%20in%20power%20till%202004.%20Ten%20years%20later%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20office.%20It%20is%20during%20his%20term%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20awarded%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20site%20to%20a%20gaggle%20of%20individuals%20and%20groups%20linked%20politically%20to%20those%20who%20brought%20the%20mosque%20down%2C%20thereby%20legally%20endorsing%20what%20the%20vandals%20were%20demanding%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20the%20temple%20is%20ready%20to%20be%20inaugurated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20obvious%20therefore%20that%20Advani%20can%20be%20credited%20%E2%80%94%20if%20that%20is%20the%20word%20%E2%80%94%20for%20not%20just%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rise%20but%20also%20the%20temple.%20To%20be%20not%20invited%20to%20its%20opening%20therefore%20must%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20that%20%E2%80%94%20Advani%20supported%20Modi%2C%20under%20whose%20rule%20Gujarat%20had%20seen%20brutal%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20in%202002%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20wanted%20to%20remove%20him.%20And%20when%20Modi%20became%20PM%2C%20he%20did%20not%20acknowledge%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20debt.%20Advani%20and%20his%20senior%20colleagues%20were%20relegated%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Margadarshak%20Mandal%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20bogus%20body%20of%20elders%20who%20would%20guide%20the%20party%2C%20which%20has%20never%20been%20heard%20of%20again.%20Putting%20them%20out%20to%20pasture%20meant%20that%20they%20have%20simply%20disappeared%20from%20public%20life.%20An%20entire%20generation%20has%20no%20clue%20who%20Advani%20or%20Joshi%20are.%20For%20them%2C%20Modi%20rises%20above%20everyone%20else%2C%20and%20he%20can%20do%20what%20he%20likes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20reading%20about%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20elders%20of%20BJP%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20society%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20respect%20senior%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20a%20question%20emerges%3A%20How%20should%20we%20react%20when%20Messrs%20Advani%20and%20Joshi%20are%20treated%20so%20disrespectfully%3F%20Should%20we%20feel%20bad%3F%20Should%20they%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20see%20the%20results%20of%20their%20hard%20work%3F%20Or%20is%20this%20just%20genuine%20concern%20about%20their%20age%20and%20health%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20journalists%20and%20others%20who%20have%20met%20Advani%20say%20he%20is%20extremely%20courteous%20and%20polite.%20Indeed%2C%20this%20is%20said%20of%20several%20BJP%20leaders%20of%20that%20era.%20Yet%2C%20somehow%2C%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20muster%20up%20any%20sympathy%20or%20righteous%20indignation%20at%20their%20plight.%20Anyone%20who%20was%20around%20at%20the%20time%20will%20recall%20India%20was%20riven%20by%20the%20Rath%20Yatra%20and%20what%20came%20after%2C%20how%20it%20brought%20out%20the%20ugliest%20in%20our%20society%2C%20and%20how%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20secular%20ethos%20was%20shattered%20in%20the%20worst%20possible%20way.%20That%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20virulent%20strain%20of%20communalism%2C%20which%20manifested%20itself%20not%20only%20as%20violence%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20but%20also%20showed%20up%20among%20urban%2C%20educated%20types%20who%20suddenly%20discovered%20their%20Hindu%20roots.%20In%20polite%20drawing%20rooms%2C%20urban%20sophisticates%20started%20talking%20about%20why%20Hindus%20needed%20to%20assert%20themselves%20in%20%E2%80%98their%20country%E2%80%99.%20Anti-minority%20sentiment%20was%20expressed%20freely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virulent%20communalism%20seen%20in%20family%20WhatsApp%20groups%20now%20had%20its%20beginnings%20then.%20Twenty-five%20years%20after%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20cynical%20Rath%20Yatra%2C%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20and%20we%20have%20all%20seen%20what%20has%20happened%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20moment%2C%20watching%20what%20we%20have%20become%20and%20where%20we%20are%20heading%2C%20we%20may%20fall%20into%20the%20trap%20of%20thinking%20those%20were%20simpler%2C%20more%20innocent%20days.%20They%20were%20not.%20The%20Rath%20Yatra%20too%20was%20a%20grab%20for%20power%20using%20religion%2C%20but%20it%20succeeded%20only%20up%20to%20a%20point.%20The%20Vajpayee%20government%20was%20in%20a%20coalition%20where%20the%20partners%20acted%20as%20a%20brake%20to%20the%20more%20nefarious%20plans%20of%20the%20BJP%20(though%20even%20then%20there%20was%20interference%20in%20education%2C%20history%20and%20culture).%20The%20institutions%20held%20steadfast%20%E2%80%94%20the%20media%20was%20not%20so%20craven%2C%20the%20judiciary%20was%20independent%20and%20Parliament%20asked%20questions.%20And%20the%20Indian%20public%2C%20unconvinced%20by%20the%20tall%20claims%20of%20India%20Shining%2C%20threw%20out%20Vajpayee%20and%20his%20government%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20have%20no%20such%20respite%2C%20no%20checks%20and%20balances.%20Much%20of%20the%20media%20lies%20prostrate%2C%20the%20judiciary%20has%20decided%20to%20fall%20in%20place%2C%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20can%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20get%20their%20act%20together%2C%20and%20most%20frightening%20of%20all%2C%20the%20Indian%20public%20is%20in%20full%20Bhakti%20mode%2C%20supporting%20the%20government%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20everything%2C%20even%20when%20its%20own%20interests%20are%20being%20hurt.%20All%20this%20is%20a%20result%20of%20that%20Rath%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20an%20%E2%80%9Celder%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20progenitor%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20is%20humiliated%20by%20his%20successors%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20feel%20bad%20for%20him.%20He%20is%20merely%20paying%20his%20dues.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703313055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fmodi-advani-e1642151298688.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-ayodhya-ram-temple-and-lk-advanis-sour-grapes-of-rath%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20difficult%20to%20feel%20sympathy%20for%20the%20man%20whose%20yatra%20has%20led%20to%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20India%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-ayodhya-ram-temple-and-lk-advanis-sour-grapes-of-rath%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mali%20recalls%20its%20envoy%20in%20Algeria%20after%20alleging%20interference%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703312014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsi