n%20December%2011.%20The%20reality%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20is%20likely%20to%20find%20itself%20pushed%20into%20a%20more%20uncertain%20political%20future%20now%20that%20the%20court%20verdict%20has%20shredded%20the%20last%20hopes%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20decision%20taken%20four%20years%20ago%20could%20be%20reversed.%20Instead%2C%20the%20impression%20cemented%20is%20that%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20independent%20institutions%20are%20themselves%20vulnerable%20to%20majoritarian%20impulses%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20this%20is%20true%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20militancy%20has%20been%20on%20a%20decline%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20since%202019%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20euphoria%20that%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20demonstrated%20recently%20might%20be%20a%20bit%20off%20the%20mark%20when%20we%20take%20a%20hard%20look%20at%20the%20state%20of%20the%20insurgency%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%207%2C%20Shah%20claimed%20that%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20had%20been%20reviewing%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20Kashmir%20every%20month.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20every%20three%20months%20I%2C%20myself%2C%20visit%20there%20and%20review%20the%20security%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20only%20terrorists%20were%20killed%2C%20but%20now%20we%20have%20destroyed%20%5Btheir%5D%20entire%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20that%20in%20less%20than%20three%20years%20from%20now%2C%20a%20complete%20%E2%80%9Carea%20domination%20plan%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20devised%20and%20implemented%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20(UT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20soft%20pedalled%20and%20nuanced%20his%20previous%20statement%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20was%20a%20source%20of%20political%20violence%20in%20the%20UT.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20said%20that%20terrorism%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20would%20end%20by%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%20I%20had%20said%20that%20with%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20there%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20reduction%20in%20separatism%20and%20due%20to%20this%2C%20terrorism%20would%20also%20reduce.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20data%20on%20militancy%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmpirically%20speaking%2C%20this%20is%20absolutely%20true%2C%20and%20is%20borne%20out%20by%20the%20statistics%20that%20Shah%20offered%20in%20parliament.%20The%20long%20trajectory%20of%20militancy%20shows%20it%20is%20experiencing%20a%20steep%20decline.%20Around%2040%2C164%20militancy%20related%20incidents%20took%20place%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20between%201994%20and%202004%2C%207%2C217%20during%20the%20following%20decade%2C%20and%20only%202%2C197%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20administration%2C%20accounting%20for%20a%20total%2070%25%20reduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20rendition%20of%20figures%20in%20this%20format%20appears%20to%20conceal%20a%20very%20crucial%20detail.%20Data%20available%20with%20the%20South%20Asia%20Terrorism%20Portal%20(SATP)%20shows%20that%20a%20precipitous%20decline%20in%20militant%20violence%20was%20already%20noticeable%20since%20the%20mid%202000s%2C%20and%20that%20militancy%20related%20incidents%20had%20dwindled%20to%20just%20245%20by%20the%20year%202014.%20(The%20figure%20stands%20at%20253%20in%20the%20year%202023%20so%20far.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20beginning%20of%20an%20uptick%20can%20be%20traced%20to%20the%20year%202016%2C%20when%20security%20forces%20gunned%20down%20the%20young%20leader%20Burhan%20Wani%2C%20infusing%20the%20militancy%20with%20new%20vigour.%20It%20is%20from%20there%20that%20militant%20activities%20escalated%2C%20culminating%20in%20the%20year%202018%20which%20was%20the%20worst%20in%20a%20decade%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20attacks%20and%20fatalities.%20And%20the%20following%20year%2C%20in%20February%202019%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpulwama-satya-pal-malik-failure-tragedy%5C%22%3EPulwama%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20killed%20over%2040%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2019%20was%20a%20major%20reboot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20Union%20government%20could%20control%20this%20spiralling%20situation%20only%20by%20placing%20over%2010%20million%20people%20under%20siege%2C%20cutting%20off%20communications%20(albeit%20briefly)%20and%20inaugurating%20an%20indiscriminate%20crackdown%20is%20telling.%20If%20this%20is%20what%20will%20ensure%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpeaceful%E2%80%9D%20Kashmir%2C%20then%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20always%20have%20to%20go%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20continue%20directly%20administering%20J%26amp%3BK.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20more%20difficult%20for%20two%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20totalitarian%20control%20which%20it%20claims%20has%20brought%20peace%20is%20fundamentally%20antithetical%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20democratic%20values%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20under%20pressure%20from%20various%20quarters%20to%20uphold%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20to%20think%20of%20it%2C%20a%20good%20number%20of%20laws%20used%20to%20police%20expression%20in%20Kashmir%20are%20actually%20emergency%20provisions%20granted%20within%20ordinary%20laws.%20Article%20311%20(2)%20(c)%20allows%20for%20terminating%20employees%2C%20sometimes%20for%20having%20written%20newspaper%20articles%20years%20ago%2C%20without%20giving%20them%20an%20opportunity%20to%20be%20heard.%20Section%20144%2C%20a%20British-era%20colonial%20law%2C%20is%20invoked%20to%20control%20various%20aspects%20of%20civil%20life%2C%20sometimes%20for%20reasons%20as%20mundane%20as%20possessing%20a%20quadcopter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%E2%80%99s%20highest%20usage%20in%20the%20country%20is%20now%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20as%20per%202021%20figures.%20And%20the%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20is%20so%20widespread%20that%20there%20is%20now%20a%20mounting%20backlog%20of%20unheard%20cases.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20this%20aspect%20earlier%20in%20June%20as%20part%20of%20its%20two-month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Frights%2Fjk-endless-wait-for-hearings-in-public-safety-act-cases-agnoises-detainees-kin%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Einvestigation%20into%20the%20use%20of%20PSA%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20any%20indication%20as%20to%20how%20arbitrary%20this%20crackdown%20can%20be%2C%20one%20only%20needs%20to%20read%20the%20bail%20orders%20of%20incarcerated%20journalists%20Fahad%20Shah%2C%20Sajad%20Gul%2C%20Aasif%20Sultan%20and%20hundreds%20of%20other%20people%20against%20whom%20very%20serious%20charges%20were%20levelled%20earlier%20but%20which%2C%20albeit%20after%20a%20prolonged%20lapse%20of%20time%2C%20came%20crashing%20down%20in%20the%20face%20of%20judicial%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24115637%2FF3-kENLboAAumNv.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24115637%2FF3-kENLboAAumNv.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24115637%2FF3-kENLboAAumNv-300x218.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24115637%2FF3-kENLboAAumNv-1024x742.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669550%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22870%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40AmitShah%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20the%20level%20playing%20field%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20reason%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20approach%20is%20unsustainable%20is%20because%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20set%20a%20time%20frame%20for%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20UT%20by%20September%202024%2C%20after%20which%20questions%20over%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20will%20grow%20shriller.%20We%20have%20already%20seen%20a%20slew%20of%20political%20manoeuvres%20intended%20to%20downsize%20the%20established%20political%20formations%20that%20are%20clearly%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20agenda.%20Delimitation%20was%20one%20such%20weapon%2C%20where%20the%20Jammu%20region%2C%20despite%20having%20a%20lower%20population%20than%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20awarded%20extra%20assembly%20seats.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20had%20nine%20more%20seats%20than%20Jammu%2C%20will%20now%20have%20only%20four%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20also%20passed%20four%20bills%20related%20to%20J%26amp%3BK.%20They%20pertain%20to%20awarding%20two%20assembly%20seats%20to%20representatives%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Kashmiri%20Migrant%E2%80%99%20community%2C%20and%20West%20Pakistan%20refugees%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20other%20bills%20also%20concern%20expanding%20the%20definition%20of%2C%20as%20well%20as%20incorporating%20more%20communities%20into%2C%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20in%20the%20UT.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20why%20the%20polls%20are%20being%20delayed%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20under%20one%20pretext%20or%20another.%20The%20BJP%20government%20wants%20to%20gerrymander%20the%20region%20to%20the%20point%20that%20it%20ends%20up%20changing%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20the%20electoral%20playing%20field%20for%20its%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20talk%20on%20holding%20urban%20local%20bodies%20(ULB)%20elections%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Then%20came%20informal%20reports%20that%20parties%20opposed%20to%20the%20BJP%20were%20likely%20to%20sweep%20any%20such%20polls.%C2%A0%20Perhaps%20that%20is%20why%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20lieutenant%20governor%20announced%20in%20November%20that%20the%20ULB%20elections%20would%20be%20delayed%20and%20will%20take%20place%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20the%20completion%20of%20delimitation%20as%20well%20as%20the%20process%20to%20reserve%20seats%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20governance%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20primarily%20been%20about%20railroading%20decisions%20that%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%20for%20the%20local%20people.%20Almost%20all%20of%20these%20decisions%2C%20whether%20about%20allowing%20non-locals%20to%20acquire%20residency%20permits%2C%20or%20delimiting%20seats%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20benefit%2C%20or%20opening%20land%20purchases%20for%20outsiders%20and%20more%2C%20are%20actually%20generating%20anxieties%20over%20the%20shrinking%20role%20that%20people%20are%20having%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMounting%20political%20despair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20is%20resulting%20in%20widespread%20political%20despair%2C%20which%20is%20seeping%20down%20to%20the%20people.%20And%20although%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20have%20largely%20been%20successful%20in%20preempting%20any%20expression%20of%20resentment%2C%20there%20was%20one%20serious%20lapse%20recently%20when%20a%20non-local%20student%20at%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20triggered%20demonstrations%20after%20an%20allegedly%20inflammatory%20social%20media%20post%20about%20Islam%E2%80%99s%20Prophet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20government%2C%20the%20protests%20probably%20rekindled%20older%20fears%20when%20the%20Nehru%20administration%2C%20through%20his%20client-politician%20Bakshi%20Ghulam%20Muhammad%2C%20was%20able%20to%20implement%20similar%20far%20reaching%20changes%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Sheikh%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20deposition%2C%20but%20ended%20up%20facing%20a%20massive%20uprising%20in%201963%20as%20the%20public%20came%20out%20in%20unprecedented%20numbers%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20theft%20of%20the%20Holy%20Relic%20associated%20with%20the%20Prophet%20in%20Srinagar.%20Such%20is%20the%20fear%20of%20protests%20today%20that%20even%20anticipated%20pro-Palestine%20demonstrations%20have%20been%20restricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20politics%20and%20militancy%20overlap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20bearing%20does%20all%20this%20have%20on%20militancy%3F%C2%A0%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20gradual%20rise%20in%20what%20law%20enforcement%20calls%20%E2%80%9Chybrid%20militancy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20shifting%20dynamics%20within%20the%20insurgency%20where%20young%20teenagers%20with%20no%20previous%20record%20are%20recruited%20as%20helpers%20for%20militants%20before%20they%20themselves%20end%20up%20perpetrating%20big%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recruiters%20mostly%20draft%20youths%20using%20encrypted%20chat%20mediums.%20They%20are%20asked%20to%20pick%20up%20weapons%20from%20a%20particular%20spot%20and%20then%20return%20it%20after%20having%20committed%20the%20attack%2C%20without%20actually%20knowing%20who%20is%20coordinating%20the%20whole%20affair.%20This%20aspect%20has%20turned%20the%20militancy%20into%20a%20more%20secretive%20affair%20where%20the%20actual%20number%20of%20recruits%20will%20always%20remain%20difficult%20to%20determine.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20security%20forces%20gunned%20down%20militant%20Abbas%20Sheikh%2C%20who%20had%20been%20instrumental%20in%20reviving%20militancy%20in%20Srinagar.%20A%20senior%20official%20told%20this%20correspondent%20that%20police%20investigations%20established%20he%20had%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20at%20least%2025-40%20young%20men%20in%20just%20the%20two%20square%20kilometres%20of%20downtown%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20%E2%80%9Chybrid%E2%80%9D%20activity%20has%20also%20come%20down%2C%20the%20dynamics%20it%20involves%20tells%20us%20that%20militant%20groups%20are%20always%20able%20to%20leverage%20the%20discontent%20within%20society%20to%20carry%20out%20high-visibility%20attacks%20like%20earlier%20in%20Rajouri%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20G20%20meeting.%20Or%20last%20month%20when%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20new%20director%20general%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20took%20office%2C%20militants%20shot%20dead%20two%20policemen%20and%20one%20labourer%20in%20three%20different%20regions%20of%20Kashmir.%20These%20attacks%20reveal%20a%20calculated%20strategy%20of%20carrying%20out%20attacks%20timed%20with%20symbolic%20political%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20changing%20faces%20of%20militancy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20hit-and-run%20killings%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Kashmir%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20have%20had%20some%20kind%20of%20involvement%20from%20these%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20correspondent%20visited%20the%20house%20of%20Natish%20Shakeel%2C%20a%2017-year-old%20militant%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20April%20last%20year%20in%20Pulwama%2C%20and%20was%20recruited%20via%20similar%20%E2%80%9Chybrid%E2%80%9D%20modules%2C%20it%20emerged%20that%20Natish%20was%20the%20grandnephew%20of%20Yousuf%20Halwai%2C%20a%20political%20leader%20associated%20with%20the%20National%20Conference%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20by%20militants.%20Asked%20what%20may%20have%20motivated%20Natish%20to%20resort%20to%20such%20a%20step%2C%20his%20uncle%2C%20among%20many%20things%2C%20blamed%20the%20choking%20of%20all%20spaces%20of%20political%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20new%20theatre%20of%20violence%20is%20opening%20up%20in%20the%20Jammu%20regions%20of%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20which%20has%20accounted%20for%2040%25%20of%20the%20total%20security%20related%20fatalities%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20this%20year.%20Last%20month%2C%20five%20soldiers%20including%20two%20captains%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Kalakote%20area%20of%20Poonch.%20This%20week%2C%20five%20soldiers%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20another%20incident%20in%20Rajouri.%20Conversations%20with%20senior%20serving%20and%20retired%20police%20officers%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20militants%20are%20trying%20to%20open%20new%20fronts%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20pivoting%20the%20focus%20away%20from%20Kashmir%20where%20they%20are%20seeking%20to%20escalate%20action%20in%20the%20future%2C%20as%20and%20when%20conducive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20political%20disillusionment%20growing%20in%20the%20Valley%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20imagine%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Czero%20terror%20plan%E2%80%9D%20working%20in%20the%20long%20term.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20tells%20us%20that%20realities%20are%20actually%20more%20convoluted%20than%20we%20care%20to%20admit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703298628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153154%2Fsrinagar-2740020_1920.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Famit-shahs-zero-terror-plan-for-jk-sounds-too-good-to-be-true-and-it-is%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government's%20actions%20have%20led%20to%20widespread%20political%20despair%20in%20Kashmir.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20that%20mood%20has%20been%20used%20by%20militants%20to%20gain%20currency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Famit-shahs-zero-terror-plan-for-jk-sounds-too-good-to-be-true-and-it-is%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stakes%20are%20immense%20as%20Biden%20presses%20Israel%20to%20change%20course%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703297796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.u