being%20raised%20by%20them%2C%20including%20demanding%20an%20official%20statement%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20the%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20security%20breach%2C%20and%20protesting%20against%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20high-handedness%2C%20mimicking%20Dhankhar%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20cheerful%20break%20for%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20other%20MPs%20enjoyed%20the%20performance%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20shot%20a%20video%20of%20it%20on%20his%20phone.%20But%20a%20majority%20of%20television%20channels%20went%20on%20an%20overdrive%20that%20Gandhi%20shot%20the%20video%20to%20circulate%20it%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20further%20heap%20insults%20on%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20the%20spin-games%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20corner%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20essential%20question%20that%20most%20have%20been%20asking%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20buried.%20Why%20has%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20not%20issued%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20the%20security%20breach%20in%20the%20Parliament%3F%20Both%20Shah%20and%20Modi%20have%20been%20giving%20interviews%20in%20the%20press%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20taken%20the%20security%20breach%20seriously%20and%20has%20ordered%20an%20inquiry.%20One%20also%20knows%20that%20the%20probe%20committee%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fitbp-dg-a-d-singh-given-additional-charge-of-crpf-9047016%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DITBP%2520Director%2520General%2520(DG)%2520Anish%2Can%2520official%2520order%2520said%2520Wednesday.%5C%22%3EAnish%20Dayal%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Director-General%20of%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%2C%20the%20very%20agency%20that%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20security%20in%20the%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20MPs%20have%20asked%20about%20a%20possible%20conflict%20of%20interest%20issue%20as%20it%20may%20not%20be%20right%2C%20at%20least%20in%20optics%2C%20for%20the%20CRPF%20Director-General%20to%20probe%20his%20own%20agency%E2%80%99s%20failure%20in%20the%20security%20breach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20the%20government%20has%20chosen%20not%20to%20address%20any%20of%20these%20concerns.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20has%20not%20attended%20a%20single%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament%20in%20December.%20Shah%2C%20who%20tabled%20the%20amended%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%20on%20Thursday%20(December%2021)%20and%20attempted%20to%20clear%20doubts%20on%20the%20new%20Bills%2C%20has%20evaded%20answering%20any%20of%20these%20serious%20questions%20in%20the%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOutside%20the%20House%2C%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20announced%20that%20the%20mimicry%20row%20shamed%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20blamed%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20for%20insulting%20the%20Jats%2C%20while%20also%20accusing%20them%20of%20shaming%20the%20Adivasis%20and%20Dalits%20when%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20and%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20were%20chosen%20as%20the%20Presidents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20quite%20rightly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fcongress-rahul-gandhi-jantar-mantar-protest-mp-suspension-9078730%2F%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20whether%20he%20should%20also%20blame%20the%20ruling%20party%20MPs%20for%20not%20letting%20him%20speak%20in%20the%20House%20because%20he%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9CDalit%E2%80%9D.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20too%2C%20attacked%20the%20government%20for%20diverting%20attention%20from%20the%20questions%20that%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20raising%20and%20asked%20whether%20the%20TMC%20MP%E2%80%99s%20mimicry%20was%20more%20important%20than%20the%20concerns%20around%20security%20breach%20and%20unpr