%20that%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20world%20history.%20An%20event%20that%20tested%20the%20resilience%20of%20the%20Nagas.%20An%20event%20that%20has%20been%20famously%20dubbed%20%E2%80%98The%20Stalingrad%20of%20the%20East%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20were%20children%2C%20my%20grandma%20would%20tell%20us%20stories%20about%20how%20she%20grew%20up%20during%20World%20War%20II%20while%20the%20British%20and%20Japanese%20soldiers%20were%20fighting%20each%20other.%20Most%20of%20our%20stories%20are%20passed%20down%20orally%20from%20one%20generation%20to%20the%20next.%20But%20in%20this%20process%2C%20they%20get%20modified%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20real%20story%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20exist%20anymore.%20In%20this%20song%2C%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20get%20the%20real%20story%20recorded%20so%20that%20it%20stays%20on%20forever%20and%20helps%20the%20younger%20generation%20understand%20what%20really%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20as%20an%20artist%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20experiment%20with%20new%20sounds%2C%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20our%20folk%20traditions.%20I%20tried%20to%20experiment%20with%20it%20while%20also%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20my%20grandma%20who%20recently%20told%20me%20more%20about%20these%20events%20while%20I%20was%20visiting%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FZWZo7LZA-KE%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc